name: Elegant Entropy
description:
A custom checkpoint mix intended to unite realistic people and breathtaking landscapes, with an emphasis on rich colors and lighting composition; and with a healthy dose of sci-fi/fantasy.

No baked-in VAE. I personally use EMA 560k, but MSE works well too.

Drop by my Discord server if you want to hang out!
